      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGICAL SAIDE (1) comes off an average run last start when seventh at this track over 450m behind Firebird (25.97) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money prior to that. Comes through a solid form race last start. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. OTHELLO (4) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 6 lengths away in third (25.72) at this track in a Grade 5 over 450m. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Must be included in calculations. ZIPPING BJORN (2) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (28.16) at Casino in a Grade 5. Has first look at box 2 this time. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Leading player again. SUNBURNT KEEPER (5) did a good job to finish third last time out over 401m at Richmond (23.08) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Safe beginner who will go forward from trap seven.",
